40
00:02:40,220 --> 00:02:41,620
Water. Thanks.

41
00:02:48,020 --> 00:02:49,780
What do you do?

42
00:02:52,460 --> 00:02:53,620
I...

43
00:02:54,620 --> 00:02:55,900
I am...

44
00:02:57,740 --> 00:02:58,540
