45
00:02:59,820 --> 00:03:01,260
I thought you were an artist.

46
00:03:03,820 --> 00:03:05,020
This is my friend's studio.

47
00:03:05,300 --> 00:03:06,500
I just resigned

48
00:03:06,500 --> 00:03:07,140
and don't have a job,

49
00:03:07,340 --> 00:03:08,100
so he let me stay here for now.

50
00:03:10,620 --> 00:03:12,300
(Why does he conceal his real identity?)

51
00:03:14,620 --> 00:03:15,820
Are you an electrician all the time?

52
00:03:16,100 --> 00:03:17,900
To be precise, I'm not one currently.

53
00:03:19,420 --> 00:03:21,020
I didn't really enjoy my last job.

54
00:03:21,220 --> 00:03:21,860
That's why I quit.

55
00:03:24,220 --> 00:03:24,580
By the way,

56
00:03:24,860 --> 00:03:26,260
I majored in electric engineering
at university.

57
00:03:26,540 --> 00:03:28,620
I'd like to find a job in this field.

58
00:03:28,980 --> 00:03:30,820
(Did he lose all the money)

59
00:03:30,820 --> 00:03:31,900
(in the family feud ?)

60
00:03:33,740 --> 00:03:35,220
Then do you plan

61
00:03:35,220 --> 00:03:36,340
to work as an electrician forever?

62
00:03:36,340 --> 00:03:38,060
