97
00:04:52,820 --> 00:04:54,380
to get a free girlfriend
to live with you.

98
00:04:55,100 --> 00:04:55,660
Hey.

99
00:05:06,220 --> 00:05:07,700
I just want a chance to look after you.

100
00:05:08,180 --> 00:05:09,620
I never thought
of doing anything bad to you.

101
00:05:10,460 --> 00:05:11,260
Please don't misunderstand me.

102
00:05:11,860 --> 00:05:13,620
The password to this door
is your birthday.

103
00:05:14,940 --> 00:05:16,140
If you don't like me staying here,

104
00:05:16,500 --> 00:05:17,340
I can move out.

105
00:05:17,820 --> 00:05:18,820
I won't be in your way.

106
00:05:23,700 --> 00:05:25,380
When you said taking responsibility
for me,

107
00:05:26,100 --> 00:05:28,260
